The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a generative adversarial network (GAN) and a parameter network also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of a discriminator to ensure the output satisfies the distribution of the target domain, which is a common technique in graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
